: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(149, 55, 52);\"></span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(141, 179, 226);\">【活动地点】</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">苏州•大运城希兰德海洋村</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(141, 179, 226);\">【活动年龄】</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">4-12岁</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(141, 179, 226);\">【活动限额】</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">1000组家庭</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(141, 179, 226);\">【活动方式】</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">自驾出行，签到入场</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(141, 179, 226);\">【活动档期】</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">4月1日至4月30日 10:00-20:30</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(251, 6, 51); font-family: Times;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 192, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体;\">----------超ོ 级ོ 滑ོ 梯ོ----------</span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(255, 192, 0);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">17米长，90度直下的</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">超级滑梯</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">爸爸妈妈都不敢挑战的刺激</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">孩儿们勇敢直下</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464941808880008.jpg\" title=\"1464941808880008.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体;\">----------职ོ 业ོ 体ོ 验ོ----------</span></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">当医生、当警察、当消防员、T台走秀</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">智力8大维度的职业体验</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">游戏之间</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">宝贝对自己的职业爱好有了模糊的认识</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464941827963792.jpg\" title=\"1464941827963792.jpg\" alt=\"5.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体;\">----------积ོ 木ོ 王ོ 国ོ----------</span></strong></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-family: 宋体;\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></strong></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">在积木池中</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">搭建梦中的王国</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">用脑、用手</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">满足自己关于童话的所有幻想</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464942011598286.jpg\" title=\"1464942011598286.jpg\" alt=\"6.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 19px; color: rgb(117, 117, 117); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\"></span></strong><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体;\">----------旋ོ 转ོ 木ོ 马ོ----------</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px; color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-family: 宋体;\"></span></strong></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\"><strong style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 0); font-size: 14px; text-align: center; white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体;\"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">拥有华丽的外表和绚的灯光</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">我是匹旋转木