 198);\">菜花</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">，时时闻到春天的气息，</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">是</span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(75, 172, 198);\">大闸蟹</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">的故乡，更是吃货的天堂。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">带着宝贝回到大自然的怀抱，</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">拥抱最美丽的天堂吧！</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160604/1465022520836797.jpg\" title=\"1465022520836797.jpg\" alt=\"2.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">-------------------活ོ 动ོ 说ོ 明ོ--------------------</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">【活动地点】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">阳澄湖莲花岛</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">【最佳年龄】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">3-12</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">岁</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">【人数限额】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">10-20</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">组</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">/</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">期</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">【预约档期】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">月</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">12</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">日、</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">13</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">日</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">&nbsp;9:30-15:30</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">【出行方式】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">自驾出行</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">-------------------活ོ 动ོ 特ོ 色ོ--------------------</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 208, 80);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">1 、</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">私҈人҈订҈制҈，个҈性҈化҈亲҈子҈游҈学҈</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 150, 70); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">携手莲花岛景区，专为宝贝和爸爸妈妈定制，个性亲子游，轻松地体验农家生活，快乐的学习渔村文化，寓教于乐，让城市生活的宝贝更能感受到大自然的魅力。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160604/1465023004787815.jpg\" title=\"1465023004787815.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 208, 80); font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">2、渔҈村҈生҈活҈，世҈外҈桃҈源҈乐҈趣҈多҈</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">最完整的保留了渔村的文化，仿佛回到三十年前，如同到了</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">“</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">世外桃源</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">”</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;\">，爸爸妈妈们回忆童年，宝贝们体验爸爸妈妈的童年时代，穿虾网，风车阵，水稻种植，还有任务线索等着宝贝来探索哦，渔家乐趣多多多。</span></span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160604/1465023122271481.jpg\" title=\"1465023122271481.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 208, 80); font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">3、春҈之҈花҈海҈，油҈菜҈花҈开҈漫҈天҈香҈</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">春之季节，花的海洋，徜徉在漫天的油菜花田中，花香四溢，满目金黄色，带着宝贝一起拥抱最自然的春天。</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><br/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal;\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160604/1465023197269584.jpg\" title=\"1465023197269584.jpg\" alt=\"5.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(146, 208, 80); font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;;\">4、别҈样҈享҈受҈，非҈凡҈的҈热҈情҈体҈验҈</span></strong></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(247, 150, 70);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center; text-i