r;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">百老汇音乐剧《猫》，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">本是剧作者韦伯根据艾略特为儿童写的诗改编的，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">经过本土创新，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">在经典童话故事基础上打造一部属于孩子的音乐剧。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464925657543283.jpg\" title=\"1464925657543283.jpg\" alt=\"3.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\"><br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464925670468153.jpg\" title=\"1464925670468153.jpg\" alt=\"4.jpg\"/>&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(26, 204, 255);\">魅ོ 力ོ 音ོ 乐ོ 剧ོ 目ོ</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">不同于普通的儿童剧，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">以音乐为主导，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">结合了歌唱、对白、表演、舞蹈等艺术形式，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">让孩子们在音乐的氛围中感受《猫》的魅力。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464925740567793.jpg\" title=\"1464925740567793.jpg\" alt=\"5.jpg\"/></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464925747501146.jpg\" title=\"1464925747501146.jpg\" alt=\"6.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(26, 204, 255);\">顶ོ 级ོ 剧ོ 组ོ 打ོ 造ོ</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">中文版百老汇音乐剧《猫》团队成员鼎力加盟，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">国内顶级儿童剧制作班底倾力打造，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">旨在创造一部本土原创的经典音乐剧目。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464925783497972.jpg\" title=\"1464925783497972.jpg\" alt=\"7.jpg\"/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(26, 204, 255);\">激ོ 发ོ 爱ོ 的ོ 共ོ 鸣ོ</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">《猫》剧故事感人至深，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">是对爱的呼唤，激发爱的共鸣，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">不仅引发家长对动物生命的敬畏和承诺，</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">更是激发孩子的伟大爱心。</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464925812361503.jpg\" title=\"1464925812361503.jpg\" alt=\"8.jpg\"/></p><p><strong style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 21px; font-family: 宋体; color: white;\">介</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 19px 19px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">一群被遗弃的流浪猫，各自有着不同的身世和故事，而如今或饥寒、或伤病、或野蛮、或卑微……白天四处藏匿，坚守着孤单寂寞，从未放弃守候希望，徘徊在对人类的依赖和不信任之间，却盼望人类那温柔的双手捧起温暖幸福。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464925849591774.jpg\" title=\"1464925849591774.jpg\" alt=\"9.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\"> 只有在夜晚明月升起时，它们相聚一起，倾诉、嬉戏、相互安慰温暖……夜晚虽短暂，徜徉着月光，就是“欢乐幸福”的。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464925859290034.jpg\" title=\"1464925859290034.jpg\" alt=\"10.jpg\"/></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 19px 19px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">它们想要留住这幸福的月光!铁匠猫、牛仔猫、神枪手、阔太猫、小偷猫……还有一只很爱惜爱惜自己尾巴的小猫，音乐响起来、舞蹈跳起来，要让月亮永不消失……</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 19px 19px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">“爱是生命的火焰，没有它，一切变成黑暗”。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px 19px 19px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(47, 47, 47); font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; font-size: 14px;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(108, 108, 108);\">&nbsp;<img src=\"http://admin.yzbtkids.com/ueditor/php/upload/image/20160603/1464925866122436.jpg\" title=\"1464925866122436.jpg\" alt=\"11.jpg\"/></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: Times; color: rgb(251, 6, 51);\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(251, 6, 51);\">月</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: Times; color: rgb(251, 6, 51);\">28</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(251, 6, 51);\">日</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(251, 6, 51);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Times; color: rgb(251, 6, 51);\">相约独墅湖影剧院</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px; font-family: Times; color: rgb(251, 6, 51);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(26, 204, 255);\">共赏百老汇四大名剧之一</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(26, 204, 255);\"></span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(26, 204, 255);\">世界经典音乐剧</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(26, 204, 255);\">《猫》</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(26, 204, 255);\">原创中文版</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Times; color: rgb(251, 6, 51);\">感悟最惊艳的舞台传奇</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align:center;text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: Times; color: rgb(251, 6, 51);\">享受最好的舞台剧启蒙</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(47, 47, 47);\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '4001184004', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1', '0', '2016-06-03 00:00:00', null);
带着孩子出去玩，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">似乎是件很麻烦的事情，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">人文，自然，娱乐，缺一不可，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">一怕人多，二怕景少，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">最怕孩子不喜欢，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">细数一下，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">还有多少没有被开发过的自然风景呢？</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">有一个地方，位于苏州西郊，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">北倚天池山，东邻木渎古镇，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">如世外桃源般保持着其最原始的风光，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">还有关于白象的美丽传说，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">在这个难得的亲子游戏时光，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">让我们一起邂逅白象湾，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">搭锅做饭，紧急逃生，默契考验，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(84, 141, 212);\">看美景花落